{
  "text": "Because of the significant involvement of emotional, cognitive, and neurological factors in IBS, a number of 2 Evidence-Based Complementary and Alternative Medicine studies have investigated psychological interventions including cognitive behavioural therapy (CBT), hypnotherapy, and relaxation exercises. An early review suggested that all of these interventions have shown benefit [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "20330257"
